text: Went down to the shop on 2 separate occasions during their opening hours, Wed and Fri. Both days shop closed even though their website indicate they are open. Called their landlines multiple times on different days also no response. Message the seller on Shoppee also no response. Very poor service and seems like the shop is waiting to close down.
Poor customer service, office run down and stocks were outdated. Staff were generally unpleasant, evident discontent with their jobs manifest in customer relations.
